Package com.st.st25sdk.type4a.st25ta

Defines all Tags classes to handle ST25TA series The ST25TA series are an NFC Forum Type 4 Tags; Tags communicate using the ISO/IEC 14443 Type A protocol.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ST25TA02KBDTag
    ST25TA02KB (Product version 0x22) with OPEN DRAIN General Purpose Output (GPO) This tag handles electronic signature included at the end of the NDEF file
    ST25TA02KBPTag
    ST25TA02KB (Product version 0x22) with CMOS General Purpose Output (GPO) This tag handles electronic signature included at the end of the NDEF file
    ST25TA02KBTag
    ST25TA02KB tag (Product version 0x22) This tag handles electronic signature included at the end of the NDEF file
    ST25TA02KDTag
    ST25TA02K with OPEN DRAIN General Purpose Output (GPO) This tag DOES NOT handle electronic signature
    ST25TA02KPTag
    ST25TA02K with CMOS General Purpose Output (GPO) This tag DOES NOT handle electronic signature
    ST25TA02KTag
    ST25TA02K tag This tag DOES NOT handle electronic signature
    ST25TA512BTag
    ST25TA512B (Product version 0x22) tag This tag handles electronic signature included in a specific file
    ST25TA512Tag
    ST25TA512 tag This tag DOES NOT handle electronic signature
    ST25TAGpoTag
    Defines all required methods to handle General Purpose Output (GPO) on ST25TA series with GPO enable
    ST25TATag
    Defines all required methods to handle ST25TA series Including Counter features
    SysFileST25TA
    Defines all required methods to handle counter feature in SYSTEM file for ST25TA series
    SysFileST25TAGpo
    Defines all required methods to handle GPO feature in SYSTEM file for ST25TA series with GPO enable only
